Recommends: python3-venv, python3-pip
Description: Translation extension for Evolution Mail
 This extension adds translation capabilities to the GNOME Evolution
 email client, enabling users to translate email message bodies
 directly within the application.
 .
 Features:
  - Offline translation using Argos Translate
  - Toggle between original and translated content
  - Support for multiple languages
  - HTML-aware translation that preserves formatting
  - Privacy-focused: no data sent to external servers
 .
 The extension uses Argos Translate for fully local, offline translation.
 No API keys are required, and all processing happens on your machine.
